### ========================
### üìÅ KATEGORI KONTEN
### ========================

### ‚úÖ GET semua kategori
GET http://localhost:3000/api/konten/kategori
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ‚úÖ POST tambah kategori
POST http://localhost:3000/api/konten/kategori
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_kategori": "Berita",
  "jenis_kategori": "Berita"
}

### ‚úÖ PUT update kategori
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/konten/kategori/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nama_kategori": "Berita Update",
  "jenis_kategori": "Berita",
  "induk_id": null
}

### ‚úÖ DELETE kategori
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/konten/kategori/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================
### üì∞ KONTEN
### ========================

### ‚úÖ GET semua konten (tanpa filter)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ‚úÖ GET konten dengan kategori, search, pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten?kategori=Berita&search=lomba&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ‚úÖ POST tambah konten
POST http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

--form
judul=Lomba 17 Agustus
deskripsi=Desa mengadakan lomba kemerdekaan
kategori=Berita
id_sub_kategori=2
id_penulis=1
status=Draft
thumbnail=@./thumb.png


### ‚úÖ GET konten by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ‚úÖ PUT update konten (ganti thumbnail)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

--form
judul=Lomba 17 Agustus Update
deskripsi=Lomba sudah dilaksanakan dan sukses
kategori=Berita
id_sub_kategori=2
id_penulis=1
status=Published
thumbnail=@./thumb-update.jpg


### ‚úÖ DELETE konten
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/konten/konten/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
